name: ActiveBleedingExcludingMensesOrBleedingDiathesis
title: Active Bleeding Excluding Menses or Bleeding Diathesis
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent concepts for active bleeding or bleeding diathesis (excluding menses).),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element related to Diagnosis.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes ICD-10CM and SNOMEDCT codes associated with active bleeding.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
